{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7a75d6e476","title":"争取今年夏季更大的丰收","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"22221b988b","index":0,"year":1959,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"7a75d6e476"}],"tags":[{"id":"89f0012853","name":"谭震林","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","name":"红旗一九五九年第四期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"de6e8c6fdb","name":"谭震林"}]},"publication_details":{"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"17901e4a07","type":"paragraph","text":"春季来临，万象更新，新的一年的农忙季节已经开始了。全国","index":0,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"1dea3fd224","type":"paragraph","text":"农民过了一年的苦战，取得了史无前例的伟大胜利之后，进行了建海在时期知用水语时理","index":1,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"64eccdcaab","type":"paragraph","text":"短期的休整，又开始按入了新的战斗。一个比一九五八车规模更大的农业生产高潮即将迅速普及全国。农业战越上的各毅领导机关，正在翻整工作部署，把力景集中到争取今年夏季更大丰收的主致方向来，打好第一仗，以保证超额完成全年的农业增产任务。","index":2,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"f295654804","type":"paragraph","text":"夺取全年胜利的第一关，也是保证今年大丰收的关键。一九五八","index":3,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"3bd510277c","type":"paragraph","text":"年的大丰收是从夏季大丰收开始","index":4,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"ed576c70ff","type":"paragraph","text":"党的八届六中全会所提出的一九五九年的纲、煤、粮、棉","index":5,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"483717eeea","type":"paragraph","text":"的，它甘经对全年大丰收想了决的生产指标和通过的关于人民","index":6,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"b591122443","type":"paragraph","text":"定的作用。去年夏收中，小麦试","index":7,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"dae1b5e5ee","type":"paragraph","text":"田亩产儿千厅的商产起录连公正若子间题的决，大大地鼓舞了全党和全国人民。各级","index":8,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"062d731a78","type":"paragraph","text":"出现，直接推动了早帮和早秋作党委凝过党代表大会、三级干","index":9,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"542da49eb2","type":"paragraph","text":"物的大丰收，对晚稽和晚秋作物部会等一系列的会龄，对今年","index":10,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"46595c9b35","type":"paragraph","text":"的大丰收也起了极为有利的影的工农业生产指标，制定了全","index":11,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"1c20bfbbea","type":"paragraph","text":"响。这一点，大家都是配忆犹新面规划，作出了具体部署。经","index":12,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"66de5ac4a3","type":"paragraph","text":"的。由于今年的粮食生产的任务过对党的六中全会决的深入","index":13,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"ebde8b75e5","type":"paragraph","text":"比去年更大，争取今年来个更大宣传和对人民公社的整顿工","index":14,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"ed9d771fae","type":"paragraph","text":"的夏季丰收，也将比去年具有更作，广大农民心情更加舒锡，","index":15,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"cb95afb875","type":"paragraph","text":"大的意义。夏粮作物以小麦为主干劲鼓得更足。全国农业先进","index":16,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"60ed152f65","type":"paragraph","text":"如果小麦的单位面积产量提高到单位代表会提出了为争取一","index":17,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"0ef1882356","type":"paragraph","text":"四百厅或大百斤，那么，三亿五子九五九年更大、更好、更全面万亩冬小麦就能够收到一于四百跃进的十大倡醛。自前全国农","index":18,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"8e7b43475c","type":"paragraph","text":"亿斤到二千一百亿斤。这样，在我","index":19,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"855ba20eaf","type":"paragraph","text":"国以小麦和杂粮为主食地区的三民正滴怀信心地为超额完成今年的农业增产指标而进行着紧","index":20,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"976fa96ee0","type":"paragraph","text":"亿五于多万人口，除了留下足够","index":21,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"ad49af6e6a","type":"paragraph","text":"的种学和供应城市的工业用粮张的劳动。","index":22,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"4c4ed1d6b8","type":"paragraph","text":"当前农业生产战鑫上的中","index":23,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"cdebff13c4","type":"paragraph","text":"副食用粮外，就完全可能使面食心任务是抓紧第一季，学取今","index":24,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"3e56d05425","type":"paragraph","text":"在整个口粮中古到很大的比重。年夏季来个更大的丰收。这是","index":25,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"bc2080b07b","type":"paragraph","text":"此外，还可能留出一定数量的小第4期","index":26,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"ee0db0ef1a","type":"paragraph","text":"13。家麦作为备粮。如果加上群划播种的五千","index":27,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"d175f118fc","type":"paragraph","text":"划扩大一千多万亩，共达一亿亩，孕均每方亩春麦，也能得到同冬小麦一样的单位","index":28,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"c9a925a183","type":"paragraph","text":"亩皮棉也要达到一百斤。还应酸看到，这面积产量，那么，我们的目子就更好过","index":29,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"cc7ed8f449","type":"paragraph","text":"是一个全国不均的数字。如果把可能发生了。对南方来配，取早霜李收，也有同","index":30,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"b4d0c5c4a2","type":"paragraph","text":"的灾害损失、自然条件的限制和工作发展样的意义。全国韵划播种早程的面积构一","index":31,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"43a03e5d76","type":"paragraph","text":"不平衡等因素估进去，那么，合年粮食亿五于万亩，如果单位面积产融提高到一","index":32,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"d0b26d3550","type":"paragraph","text":"作物南产千斤以上的面积，就必须从去年子到一-千五百斤，就可以收到一一千五百亿","index":33,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"a1886c9d95","type":"paragraph","text":"占播种面积的百分之儿增加到百分之五十到二千二百五十亿厅。我们抓好了第一","index":34,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"6e1ca41443","type":"paragraph","text":"左右，皮棉就必须有相当大的面积达到亩委，就有可能使夏粮和早稍的总产量达到","index":35,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"06e2e09096","type":"paragraph","text":"产一百五下斤以上，才能保都完成和超二千九百亿到四子三百五十亿斤。加上粉","index":36,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"8984c883bf","type":"paragraph","text":"完成今车药农业境产任务。七千万商大麦、元麦，蚕豆、源豆和薯","index":37,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"8ff6767405","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年农业生产任务的互性还类，就有可能接近或超过一九五七年的粮","index":38,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"b44ab298f8","type":"paragraph","text":"泰现在农村劳动力的紧张上。今年不但要食总产量，面且主要是翻粮。这就是，","index":39,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"f8baa521d7","type":"paragraph","text":"求粮棉大增产，而且要求农林牧副流全抓好了第一季，就有可能解决全年的口粮","index":40,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e476"},{"id":"64d3608d9c","type":"paragraph","text":"大革命和冠办工业的大发展。农业本身也周题；同时也必然会大大援奋人心，寿","index":41,"publicationId":"c134bfb6-984f-4ae1-bdee-bfad58ca928c","articleId":"7a75d6e47